    "description": "In &quot;The Risen Survival,&quot; you find yourself in the midst of a captivating survival adventure. The game begins with your main character awakening in the heart of a dense, mysterious forest. Disoriented and with no recollection of the past several months, your character must navigate this treacherous environment to uncover the truth about their past and find a way back home.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>HUNT</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265370/extras/0aeb4327dc3c1bcd259a9c1d1ef2f756.poster.avif?t=1689036080\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265370/extras/0aeb4327dc3c1bcd259a9c1d1ef2f756.webm?t=1689036080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265370/extras/0aeb4327dc3c1bcd259a9c1d1ef2f756.mp4?t=1689036080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Successful hunting not only provides sustenance but also yields valuable resources such as meat, fur, or bones that can be used for crafting.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>GATHER</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265370/extras/b7185566136f22a555710423a6a6e175.poster.avif?t=1689036080\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265370/extras/b7185566136f22a555710423a6a6e175.webm?t=1689036080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265370/extras/b7185566136f22a555710423a6a6e175.mp4?t=1689036080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Players must carefully balance their time and energy while being mindful of their surroundings to ensure they gather enough resources to thrive in the harsh wilderness and overcome the obstacles they encounter.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>BUILD</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265370/extras/021d6f8a5bf867613d53d4c4b258efcc.poster.avif?t=1689036080\" width=614 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265370/extras/021d6f8a5bf867613d53d4c4b258efcc.webm?t=1689036080\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2265370/extras/021d6f8a5bf867613d53d4c4b258efcc.mp4?t=1689036080\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>From simple wooden huts to elaborate fortresses, the building mechanic offers creative freedom, strategic planning, and problem-solving.<br><br>soon we will update more here.",
